---
import Placeholder from './ui/Placeholder.astro';
import Button from './ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-rice-paper relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
         <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
             <!-- Content -->
             <div class="space-y-8">
                 <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal-ink">
                     The Walled Garden<br />
                     <span class="text-olive-growth italic font-medium">(With an Open Gate)</span>
                 </h2>

                 <div class="prose prose-lg text-charcoal-ink/90 font-body">
                     <p>
                        BonsAI is a local vault. We use a standard SQLite database (<code>bonsai.db</code>) stored on your machine.
                     </p>
                     <p class="font-bold text-xl mt-4 mb-2">The Harvest Protocol</p>
                     <p>
                        We believe the best way to keep you is to let you leave. Use the 'Harvest' command to export your entire history, memory, and personas into universal Markdown and JSON files. Your data is yours, forever.
                     </p>
                 </div>

                 <ul class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm border-t-2 border-charcoal-ink/10 pt-8">
                     <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full"></span>
                         Zero Telemetry (We don't know you exist)
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full"></span>
                         Firewall Friendly (Block us, we still work)
                     </li>
                     <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                         <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-olive-growth rounded-full"></span>
                         Standard File Formats (Markdown/JSON)
                     </li>
                 </ul>
             </div>

             <!-- Visual -->
             <div class="relative">
                 <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-terracotta/10 rounded-full blur-2xl z-0"></div>
                 <Placeholder 
                    type="image" 
                    caption="Fig 4: One-click export of your entire digital brain."
                    class="relative z-10 rotate-1 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500"
                 />
             </div>
         </div>
    </div>
</section>
